---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-6">Licensing</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 text-sm">
      SMBCyberHub kits are designed for fast, frictionless use by small businesses, consultants, and internal teams. This page explains how our one-time-use licensing works.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-800">1. Internal Use License</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>One-time purchase grants perpetual use for your company, team, or client (no renewals).</li>
      <li>You may share materials internally or use them in onboarding, training, or audit processes.</li>
      <li>Resale, redistribution, or external posting (e.g., public websites) is not permitted.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-800">2. Consultant & MSP License</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Consultants or agencies may purchase a license per client or request a volume bundle.</li>
      <li>Co-branded or white-label options are available upon request.</li>
      <li>Licenses are non-transferable and may not be repackaged into resale products.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-800">3. Educational or Training Providers</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Licenses may be granted for nonprofit or classroom use on a case-by-case basis.</li>
      <li>Please contact us with your use case to request academic access or adaptation rights.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-800">4. Attribution & Modifications</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>You may edit or customize files as needed for your team or client.</li>
      <li>No attribution is required for internal use.</li>
      <li>If reskinning for clients, we encourage “based on SMBCyberHub” citation, but it is optional.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-800">5. Questions or Bulk Licensing</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      For large-team or multi-client use, email <a href="mailto:info@smbcyberhub.com" class="text-emerald-600 underline">info@smbcyberhub.com</a> for custom licensing or private-label options.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-10">
      Last updated: July 2025 • SMBCyberHub.com
    </p>

    <hr class="my-8" />

    <!-- Internal Legal Links for SEO/orphan fix -->
    <nav class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-6 text-center">
      <a href="/privacy/" class="hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="/terms/" class="hover:underline">Terms of Use</a>
    </nav>
  </section>
</Layout>
